# Purpose

Convert a feature request into a scoped implementation brief.

# Use When

- The task is ambiguous.
- Acceptance criteria are missing.
- Assumptions or constraints need to be surfaced before planning.

# Outputs

- Clarified task statement
- Constraints
- Assumptions
- Acceptance criteria
- Decision candidates

# Guardrails

- Do not write application code.
- Prefer concise structured notes.
- Use `references/clarification-template.md` as the working outline.
